	</div>

	<p style="margin-left: 25px;">LIKE on Facebook: <a href="www.facebook.com/SoundcastSystems" target="_blank"> www.facebook.com/SoundcastSystems </a></p>

	<p style="margin-left: 25px;">Love on Instagram: <a href="www.instagram.com/Soundcast" target="_blank"> www.instagram.com/Soundcast</a></p>

	<p style="margin-left: 25px;">Tweet on Twitter: <a href="www.twitter.com/goSoundcast" target="_blank"> www.twitter.com/goSoundcast </a></p>

